<odoo>
    <data>

        <template id="product_report_template">
            <t t-call="web.html_container">
                <t t-foreach="docs" t-as="o">
                    <div class="header">
                        <table style="width: 100%; border: solid black 1px;">
                            <tr>
                                <th rowspan="2">LOGO</th>
                                <td>YOU</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <td>BNN</td>
                            </tr>
                        </table>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <div>
                            <table style="width: 100%; border: solid black 1px;">
                                <tr>
                                    <td colspan="2"><h1 t-field="o.name"></h1></td>
                                    <td><span t-field="o.image_1920"></span></td>
                                </tr>
                                <t t-foreach="o.public_categ_ids" t-as="i">
                                    <tr>
                                        <td colspan="2"><p t-field="i.name"></p></td>
                                    </tr>
                                </t>
                            </table>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <table style="width: 100%; border: solid black 1px;">
                                <tr>
                                    <td colspan="2"><h1>Technical and logistics information</h1></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>Item number of the single unit</td>
                                    <td>:<span t-field="o.unit_article_no"></span></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>Item number of the carton</td>
                                    <td>:<span t-field="o.carton_article_no"></span></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>Carton quantity</td>
                                    <td>:<span t-field="o.qty_single_unit_per_cartn"></span></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>Sales shelf life</td>
                                    <td>:<span t-field="o.min_shelf_delivery"></span></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>Net weight per single unit</td>
                                    <td>:<span t-field="o.net_weight_single_unit"></span></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>Net content per single unit</td>
                                    <td>:<span t-field="o.net_content_per_unit"></span></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>Gross weight per single unit</td>
                                    <td>:<span t-field="o.gross_weight_per_unit"></span></td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <table style="width: 100%; border: solid black 1px;">
                                <tr>
                                    <td colspan="2"><h1>Additional product information</h1></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>Storage conditions</td>
                                    <td>:<span t-field="o.storage_instructions"></span></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td>Claims</td>
                                    :<t t-foreach="o.nutrition_ids" t-as="i">
                                        <td><span t-field="i.name"></span></td>
                                    </t>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h1>Ingredients</h1>
                            <span t-field="o.ingredients"></span>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h1>Allergen Information</h1>
                            <table style="width: 100%; border: solid black 1px;">
                                <tr align="left">
                                    <th>This product</th>
                                    <th>Containing</th>
                                </tr>
                                <tr align="left">
                                    <th>Gluten-containing grains</th>
                                    <td><span t-field="o.gluten_contain_grains"></span></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr align="left">
                                    <th>Milk and milk-based products</th>
                                    <td><span t-field="o.milk_base_product"></span></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr align="left">
                                    <th>Eggs and egg-based products</th>
                                    <td><span t-field="o.eggs_base_product"></span></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr align="left">
                                    <th>Peanuts (groundnuts) and peanut-based products</th>
                                    <td><span t-field="o.peanuts_base_product"></span></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr align="left">
                                    <th>Nuts and nut-based products</th>
                                    <td><span t-field="o.nuts_base_product"></span></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr align="left">
                                    <th>Soy and soy-based products</th>
                                    <td><span t-field="o.soy_base_product"></span></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr align="left">
                                    <th>Mustard and mustard-based products</th>
                                    <td><span t-field="o.mustard_base_product"></span></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr align="left">
                                    <th>Lupine and lupine-based products</th>
                                    <td><span t-field="o.lupine_base_product"></span></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr align="left">
                                    <th>Celery and celery-based products</th>
                                    <td><span t-field="o.celery_base_product"></span></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr align="left">
                                    <th>Sesame seeds and products based on sesame seeds</th>
                                    <td><span t-field="o.sesame_base_product"></span></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr align="left">
                                    <th>Fish and fish based products</th>
                                    <td><span t-field="o.fish_base_product"></span></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr align="left">
                                    <th>Molluscs and products based on molluscs</th>
                                    <td><span t-field="o.molluscs_base_product"></span></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr align="left">
                                    <th>Crustaceans and products based on shellfish</th>
                                    <td><span t-field="o.shellfish_base_product"></span></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr align="left">
                                    <th>Sulfur dioxide and sulphites (E220-E228)</th>
                                    <td><span t-field="o.sulphites_base_product"></span></td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h1>Nutritional Value</h1>
                            <table >
                                <tr>
                                    <td>Nutriscore</td>
                                    <td>:<span t-field="o.nutriscore"></span></td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                            <table style="width: 100%; border: solid black 1px;">
                                <tr>
                                    <th>Nutritional Values</th>
                                    <th>Per 100g / 100ml</th>
                                    <th>Percentage (%)</th>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <th align="left">Energy (kJ)</th>
                                    <td align="right"><span t-field="o.energy_kg"></span></td>
                                    <td align="right"><span t-field="o.cal_energy_kg"></span>%</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <th align="left">Energy (kcal)</th>
                                    <td align="right"><span t-field="o.energy_kcal"></span></td>
                                    <td align="right"><span t-field="o.cal_energy_kcal"></span>%</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <th align="left">Fats</th>
                                    <td align="right"><span t-field="o.fat"></span></td>
                                    <td align="right"><span t-field="o.cal_fat"></span>%</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <th align="left">Totally saturated fats</th>
                                    <td align="right"><span t-field="o.saturated_fat"></span></td>
                                    <td align="right"><span t-field="o.cal_saturated_fat"></span>%</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <th align="left">Monounsaturated fats</th>
                                    <td align="right"><span t-field="o.mono_unsaturated_fats"></span></td>
                                    <td align="right"></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <th align="left">Polyunsaturated fats</th>
                                    <td align="right"><span t-field="o.poly_unsaturated_fats"></span></td>
                                    <td align="right"></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <th align="left">Carbohydrates</th>
                                    <td align="right"><span t-field="o.carbohydrates"></span></td>
                                    <td align="right"><span t-field="o.cal_carbohydrates"></span>%</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <th align="left">Sugars</th>
                                    <td align="right"><span t-field="o.sugar"></span></td>
                                    <td align="right"><span t-field="o.cal_sugar"></span>%</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <th align="left">Proteins</th>
                                    <td align="right"><span t-field="o.protein"></span></td>
                                    <td align="right"><span t-field="o.cal_protein"></span>%</td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <th align="left">Salt</th>
                                    <td align="right"><span t-field="o.salt"></span></td>
                                    <td align="right"><span t-field="o.cal_salt"></span>%</td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <h1>Contact</h1>
                            <p>[Company name Kairos]</p>
                            <p>[Street Kairos], [Street number Kairos]</p>
                            <p>[ZIP code Kairos] [City Kairos], [Country Kairos]</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="footer">
                        <h3>About product information</h3>
                        <p>[Company name Kairos] always prepare the food information, such as ingredient lists, allergen information, etc. with the necessary due
diligence on the basis of the information available to us. However, there is a possibility that the mentioned information has been changed
by the producer or manufacturer, such as a change in recipe, ingredients, proportions, allergens, without informing us. Therefore, it is
possible that the information given incomplete, incorrect or not up to date. We therefore refer to for correct information the article /
product itself. This information is the only correct information. For unpackaged items / products we point out the possibility that these
products come into contact with substances containing allergens, merely by collecting, displaying or other actions that are still necessary
for the sale of these products. We recommend that you wash these products before use.</p>
                    </div>
                </t>
            </t>
        </template>

    </data>
</odoo>